    <string name="about_text">
       <![CDATA[
        <h3>About:</h3>
        Meals is an useful and simple meal budgeting tool. After providing a
        starting and current balance, and a end date for the budget period,
        Meals determine a daily allowance. If you spend the recommended amount
        per day you will be able to spend all of your budget.
        <br/>
        Meals also provides an estimate for the remaining fund this week and
        month. Allowing you to easily purchase food for a longer period without
        the worry of going over budget.
